Name
       timing_path_based_report_analysis_summary_max_paths_limit

Syntax
       timing_path_based_report_analysis_summary_max_paths_limit <integer >

       Default: 2000000

       Sets a limit on the maximum number of paths that can be reported in PBA
       mode with the report_analysis_summary command.

       To set this global variable, use the set command.

